  "content": "<section class=\"seedance-article\">\n\n<style>\n/* ===== الأساس ===== */\nhtml{\n  transition:background .3s ease,color .3s ease;\n}\n\nbody{\n  margin:0;\n  font-family:'Tajawal',sans-serif;\n  background:#0b0c11;\n  color:#ffffff;\n  transition:.3s ease;\n  font-size:13px;\n}\n\n/* ===== الوضع النهاري الكامل ===== */\nhtml.light-mode body{\n  background:#f4f6fb;\n  color:#111;\n}\n\n/* ===== زر عائم يسار دائمًا ===== */\n.seedance-theme-toggle{\n  position:fixed;\n  top:14px;\n  left:14px;\n  z-index:9999;\n}\n\n.seedance-theme-toggle button{\n  width:34px;\n  height:34px;\n  border-radius:50%;\n  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);\n  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\n  backdrop-filter:blur(14px);\n  -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(14px);\n  color:#ffffff;\n  font-size:14px;\n  cursor:pointer;\n  display:flex;\n  align-items:center;\n  justify-content:center;\n  transition:.3s ease;\n  box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n}\n\n.seedance-theme-toggle button:hover{\n  transform:scale(1.1);\n}\n\nhtml.light-mode .seedance-theme-toggle button{\n  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\n  color:#111;\n  border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\n\n/* ===== الحاوية ===== */\n.seedance-article{\n  width:100%;\n  padding:90px 0 60px 0;\n}\n\n.seedance-card{\n  width:100%;\n  padding:40px 5%;\n  box-sizing:border-box;\n  transition:.3s ease;\n}\n\nhtml.light-mode .seedance-card{\n  background:#ffffff;\n}\n\n/* ===== فيديو Shorts طولي ===== */\n.seedance-video{\n  width:100%;\n  max-width:380px;\n  margin:0 auto 25px auto;\n  aspect-ratio:9/16;\n  border-radius:16px;\n  overflow:hidden;\n}\n\n.seedance-video iframe{\n  width:100%;\n  height:100%;\n  border:none;\n}\n\n/* ===== العنوان ===== */\n.seedance-title{\n  font-size:14px;\n  font-weight:700;\n  text-align:center;\n  margin-bottom:18px;\n}\n\n/* ===== انفجار متحرك ===== */\n.boom{\n  display:inline-block;\n  animation:boomPulse 1.2s infinite ease-in-out;\n}\n\n@keyframes boomPulse{\n  0%{transform:scale(1);}\n  50%{transform:scale(1.25) rotate(8deg);}\n  100%{transform:scale(1);}\n}\n\n/* ===== النص ===== */\n.seedance-text{\n  font-size:13px;\n  line-height:1.9;\n  margin-bottom:16px;\n  text-align:center;\n}\n\n/* ===== بطاقة المميزات ===== */\n.seedance-features{\n  width:100%;\n  margin:20px 0;\n  padding:18px;\n  border-radius:14px;\n  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\n  line-height:1.9;\n  font-size:13px;\n}\n\nhtml.light-mode .seedance-features{\n  background:#f1f3f7;\n}\n\n/* ===== الوسوم ===== */\n.seedance-tags{\n  margin-top:20px;\n  text-align:center;\n  font-size:12px;\n  opacity:.8;\n}\n\n/* ===== CTA ===== */\n.seedance-cta{\n  margin-top:25px;\n  text-align:center;\n}\n\n.seedance-cta-title{\n  font-size:13px;\n  margin-bottom:10px;\n}\n\n.seedance-cta a{\n  display:inline-block;\n  padding:8px 22px;\n  font-size:12px;\n  background:#3fa9ff;\n  color:#fff;\n  text-decoration:none;\n  border-radius:18px;\n  transition:.3s ease;\n}\n\n.seedance-cta a:hover{\n  background:#2d8be0;\n}\n</style>\n\n<!-- زر -->\n<div class=\"seedance-theme-toggle\">\n  <button onclick=\"toggleTheme()\" id=\"themeIcon\">🌙</button>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"seedance-card\">\n\n<div class=\"seedance-video\">\n  <iframe \n    src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9eUJYOjVmYs\"\n    allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\"\n    allowfullscreen\n    loading=\"lazy\">\n  </iframe>\n</div>\n\n<h1 class=\"seedance-title\">\nهوليوود في مأزق حقيقي <span class=\"boom\">💥</span>\n</h1>\n\n<p class=\"seedance-text\">\nهذا هو Seedance 2.0… النموذج الذي لا يكتفي بتجاوز الوادي الغريب، بل يمحوه تمامًا.\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"seedance-text\">\nالواقعية هنا صادمة إلى حد يصعب تجاهله:\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"seedance-features\">\n<strong>المميزات الرئيسية</strong><br><br>\n🔹 تعبيرات دقيقة جدًا تشبه الإنسان الحقيقي<br>\n🔹 إحساس بالوزن والحركة يجعل الجسد يبدو طبيعيًا<br>\n🔹 حوارات نابضة بالحياة تشعرك أنك أمام ممثل حقيقي\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"seedance-text\">\nلم يعد هناك ما يصرخ: هذا ذكاء اصطناعي.\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"seedance-tags\">\n#الذكاء_الاصطناعي #Seedance #توليد_الفيديو\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"seedance-cta\">\n  <div class=\"seedance-cta-title\">الموقع الرسمي لـ Seedance</div>\n  <a href=\"https://seedance2.ai/\" target=\"_blank\">اضغط هنا</a>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<script>\nfunction toggleTheme(){\n  const root=document.documentElement;\n  const btn=document.getElementById('themeIcon');\n\n  root.classList.toggle('light-mode');\n\n  if(root.classList.contains('light-mode')){\n    btn.textContent='☀';\n    localStorage.setItem('theme','light');\n  }else{\n    btn.textContent='🌙';\n    localStorage.setItem('theme','dark');\n  }\n}\n\nwindow.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',()=>{\n  const savedTheme=localStorage.getItem('theme');\n  const btn=document.getElementById('themeIcon');\n  if(savedTheme==='light'){\n    document.documentElement.classList.add('light-mode');\n    btn.textContent='☀';\n  }\n});\n</script>\n\n</section>",
